snippet.title: The Strongest TOFU Full Game Walkthrough - No Commentary
snippet.description: Be The TOFU. The one and only Tofu action game created by a real Tofu Meister. You choose one of three varieties, and in its endless journey it gradually softens, crumbles, stews, and acquires bittern to become TOFU.
